'''果作语'''是中国[[云南省|云南省]][[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]]和[[绿春县|绿春县]]一种[[哈尼语支|哈尼语支]]语言。

果作语由施建光(2011)记录。

==分布==
在[[绿春县|绿春县]], 果作语使用于平河区的下列村(''绿春县志'' 1992):<ref>云南省绿春县志编纂委员会编纂. 1992. 绿春县志. 昆明: 云南民族出版社.</ref>车里、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122004|title=绿春县平河乡车里村委会|website=www.ynszxc.net|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230194918/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122004|dead-url=no}}</ref>新寨、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122066|title=绿春县平河乡新寨村委会|website=www.ynszxc.net|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230193215/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122066|dead-url=no}}</ref>东哈、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122012|title=绿春县平河乡东哈村委会|website=www.ynszxc.net|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230190323/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122012|dead-url=no}}</ref>则东。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122044|title=绿春县平河乡东批村委会则东村|website=www.ynszxc.net|access-date=2021-03-30|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230191538/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=122044|dead-url=no}}</ref>

''金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县民族志''(2013:89, 101)<ref>金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县民族志1979-2010. 金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县民族宗教事务局编. 云南民族出版社. 2013年8月. {{ISBN|9787536757028}}</ref>报告国昨语(郭卓语<ref name="Almanac">''金平县志'' (1994)</ref>)在者米、勐拉和金水河等乡使用，截至2005年包括1,953户和8,398人。Shi (2011)记录了[[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]]金水河镇普角村果作方言。<ref name="Guozuo">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=188115 |title=金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县金水河镇普角村委会 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230233301/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vindex.aspx?departmentid=188115 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

''哈尼族社会历史调查''(2009)报告格邹语分布在[[金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县|金平苗族瑶族傣族自治县]]下列村(''注释''：哈尼村名在汉村名前)：<ref>《中国少数民族社会历史调查资料丛刊》修订编辑委员会. 2009. ''哈尼族社会历史调查'', p.61. Beijing: 民族出版社.</ref>
*三区: 里加扎(翁当寨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188931 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230193113/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188931 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)、那纽普玛(大其寨<ref name="ynszxc.net">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188918 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230193241/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188918 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)、那纽扎(小其寨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188919 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230193818/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188919 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188920 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230184638/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188920 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)
*四区: 苟切扎(五了果寨)、斯楼丘扎(独果寨)、达普扎(平安寨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188722 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230190227/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=188722 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)、切玛扎(河边寨<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=189347 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2018-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230185941/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=189347 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)、吴普扎(新安寨)

